<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Letter of Reference Request</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #000;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: flex-start;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #000;
            padding-bottom: 5px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .header-left, .header-right {
            width: 48%; /* Adjust as needed to match the image */
        }
        .header p {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            line-height: 1.2;
        }
        .header-left p:first-child,
        .header-right p:first-child {
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 2px;
        }
        .header-left p:last-child,
        .header-right p:last-child {
            font-size: 0.8em;
        }
        .content {
            text-align: justify;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            text-align: left;
        }
        ul {
            padding-left: 20px;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <div class="header-left">
            <p><strong>Prof. T. Laxminidhi, Dean (FW)</strong></p>
            <p>deanfw@nitk.edu.in</p>
        </div>
        <div class="header-right">
            <p><strong>National Institute of Technology Karnataka, Surathkal, Mangaluru - 575025</strong></p>
            <p>(An Institute of National Importance, Established under NITSER Act, Government of India)</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <p>4<sup>th</sup> October, 2024</p>

        <p>To, <br>
        <%=@name.content %><br>
        <%=@aff.content%><br>
        <%=@email.content%></p>

        <p>Dear Professor,</p>

        <p><strong>Sub: Letter of Reference</strong></p>

        <p>Greetings, and hope you are doing well. May I request you to email me a confidential letter of reference
        for Dr. <%=@can_name.content%>, who has applied for a faculty position at NITK and given your name as a
        referee. The candidate has been short-listed for the selection committee interviews, which are planned
        starting from mid-October, 2024.</p>

        <p>As you may be aware, NITK Surathkal is an Institute of National Importance, ranked among the top 20
        engineering colleges in India (NIRF 2023). It has over 7000 students and 270 faculty members from
        different parts of India. Faculty are expected to engage in world-class teaching, mentoring, research,
        innovation and outreach activities, contributing to Institute's growth as well as social impact.</p>

        <p>NITK had recently invited applications from qualified Indian Nationals and Overseas Citizens of India for
        faculty positions in various disciplines. We are looking for outstanding researchers with high credentials,
        capability and track record of excellence in the above-mentioned activities.</p>

        <p>In this context, your letter of reference will greatly help us to judge the suitability of the candidate. Please
        assess the following aspects (both strengths and weaknesses, with brief examples, if possible):</p>

        <ul>
          <strong><li>Domain Knowledge</strong> - breadth & depth; intra-, inter- & trans- disciplinary, etc.</li>
          <strong><li>Research & Impact</strong> - publications, projects, patents, practical application, etc.</li>
          <strong><li>Teaching Ability</strong> - fundamentals, communication skill, handling questions, etc.</li>
          <strong><li>Attitude & Empathy</strong> - open to ideas, collaboration-friendly, understanding, helpful.</li>
        </ul>

        <p>We understand that you may have a busy schedule, but request you to kindly send the reference letter
        within 10 days for timely evaluation. Your support in this matter is greatly appreciated. Please feel free
        to contact me if you have any questions or need clarifications.</p>

        <p>Thank you in advance for your time and consideration.</p>

   <div class="footer">
            <p>Best Regards,</p>
            <p>T. Laxminidhi<br>
            Dean (Faculty Welfare)<br>
            E-Mail: deanfw@nitk.edu.in<br>
            M: +91 94805 75653</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>